Authorization
=============
Authentication ==> it will check the user is valid or not
Authorization==> the user is  valid but he will check the access privetlization it will check permission

Types Of Authentication
==================
1) Basic Authentication
2) Digest Authentication
3) Preemptive  Authentication
4) Bearer  Token Authentication
4) oAuth 1.0, 2.0 Authentication
5) API keys Authentication

auth methods we can pass in the any type of authentication

note basic,digest and preemptive authentications are use user name and password but internally algarithem is defferent